                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-sm">
                KrutiDev ↔ Unicode
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-5 flex-grow">
              The standard KrutiDev to Unicode Devanagari conversion for modern systems, web publishing, and search visibility.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-2 mt-auto">
