            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-600 dark:border-brand-500 bg-slate-100/50 dark:bg-slate-900/40 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
            <h3 class="font-extrabold text-sm text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-1">
              Hindi typing exam candidates & teachers
            </h3>
            <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-650 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Convert KrutiDev-formatted practice material and question 
              papers into Unicode for use on modern exam systems, or vice versa 
