              Publishers, translators & content creators
            </h3>
            <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-650 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Digitise Hindi archives, convert scanned OCR output from 
              legacy fonts, or prepare Devanagari content for websites, apps, and 
              social media where Unicode is required.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- SECTION 5 — HOW TO CONVERT KRUTIDEV ONLINE -->
      <section class="border-t border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-800/60 pt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 tracking-tight mb-2">
          How to convert KrutiDev online — step by step
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Our online KrutiDev converter is designed to be usable without 
          any technical knowledge. Here's the complete process:
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
